  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  itemId: 3
  indentLevel: 0
  storyText: 'Hi there! I''m an "Idle NPC" {wc}

    You normally find me in games
    standing in a given spot and just giving you directons, quests or just as your
    general trader! {wc}

    I don''t even have a State Machine, I''m just a GameObject
    with an Animator set to play my Idle animation.'
